Package gobblin.data.management.version.finder

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    VersionFinder<T extends DatasetVersion>
    Finds dataset versions.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDatasetVersionFinder<T extends FileSystemDatasetVersion>
    Class to find FileSystemDataset versions in the file system.
    AbstractHiveDatasetVersionFinder
    An abstract VersionFinder to create HiveDatasetVersions for all Partitions of a HiveDataset.
    DatasetVersionFinder<T extends FileSystemDatasetVersion>
    Class to find FileSystemDataset versions in the file system.
    DatePartitionHiveVersionFinder
    A Hive Partition finder where the the version is the partition value.
    DateTimeDatasetVersionFinder
    DatasetVersionFinder for datasets based on path timestamps.
    FileLevelTimestampVersionFinder
    VersionFinder that uses the most nested file, or directory if no file exists, level modifiedTimestamp under the datasetRoot path to find FileSystemDatasetVersions, and represents each version as TimestampedDatasetVersion using the file level path and modifiedTimestamp.
    GlobModTimeDatasetVersionFinder
    Finds FileSystemDatasetVersions using a glob pattern.
    ModDateTimeDatasetVersionFinder
    VersionFinder for datasets based on modification timestamps.
    SingleVersionFinder
    Implementation of VersionFinder that uses a StringDatasetVersion and simply creates a single StringDatasetVersion for the given FileSystemDataset.
    UnixTimestampVersionFinder
    Implementation of VersionFinder that generates TimestampedDatasetVersion from a unix timestamp in the name of each version path.
    WatermarkDatasetVersionFinder
    Finds watermarked dataset versions as direct subdirectories of the dataset directory.
